701
00:41:56,960 --> 00:42:03,120
{\an9}♪ Have yourself a merry little Christmas ♪

702
00:42:03,970 --> 00:42:08,040
{\an9}♪ Let your heart be light ♪

703
00:42:11,180 --> 00:42:18,050
{\an9}♪ From now on, our troubles will be out of sight ♪

